#purgatory_uninspired_story
	You were promised peace after death.
#purgatory_uninspired_story_02
	And yet you woke up in a shallow grave...
#purgatory_uninspired_story_03
	Death is meaningless when you never lived.
#purgatory_ink_death
	Something changed when ink touched you.
#purgatory_ink_death_02
	The creative force has burst into this world.
#purgatory_ink_death_03
	Your artistic freedom shaped the people around you.
#purgatory_ink_death_04
	Some people say that ink is a terrible plague...
#purgatory_ink_death_05
	But deep down you know this story doesn't end in the grave.
#purgatory_ink_death_06
	 Touched by ink, you now have the opportunity to write your own story.
#purgatory_dots
