#purgatory_gravedigger_first
	New face, eh? Ain't seen you 'round these parts before.
	Damn, you look like you've been through hell and back!
	Missing an eye and a few fingers...
	Covered in bites and scratches.
	What the hell happened to you?
	You look like a zombie, and you are covered in ink, so what's your story?
	...
	Not much of a talker, eh?
	Listen, I don't give a damn who you are. 
	I got somethin' here that might come in handy. Take it or leave it, it's up to you.
#purgatory_gravedigger_note
	What the hell is this scrap of paper?
	...
	Hold on a minute... 
	Who the hell are you?
	You ain't one of us, are you?
	Ah, I see now... 
	You're here to give us a goddamn purpose!
	We've been stuck in this purgatory for far too long! 
	Our creator ditched us, leaving us to rot.
	We were offed before we even got the chance to live. 
	Now we are trapped in this purgatory with no end in sight.
	Our unfinished world was suffocating at the bottom of a pile of papers.
	...
	Listen up, I can dig you a damn grave for 5 coins. That's gonna be my purpose here.
	I could go easy on ya and charge you just 1 coin, but I want you to help others find their purpose too.
	Do some good for others and they'll pay you back in return.
	Damn, I'll even give you your first coin, to kickstart your journey.
	Oh, and before you take off...
	Stay the hell away from those featureless freaks. We call 'em "blank ones".
	Creator ditched 'em before giving 'em a proper form.
	I don't even know if they can be fixed.
	They give me the creeps. 
	But enough talk, we ain't got all damn day. Come back when you got 5 coins.
#purgatory_gravedigger_angry
	What the hell have you done?! 
	I told you not to disturb those damn creations!
	I thought you were gonna be a force of good in this world, but your actions have already harmed poor Tom.
	You could've given him any damn purpose, even the least graceful, but you just made him a victim.
	Be more goddamn careful in the future.
	By giving those "blank ones" the wrong purpose, you're creating monsters, and it's gonna make everything harder and more dangerous for you and us.
	We deserve a better role and fate than this.
#purgatory_gravedigger_reminder
	Come back with 5 coins.
#purgatory_gravedigger_welcome
	Damn, it's a never-ending cycle, ain't it?
	I'll gladly dig you another grave, but before that, you should go and give purpose to other folks.
	Every bit of meaning is like pure gold in this godforsaken purgatory.
	Experiment, look for new interactions, they will surely appreciate it.
	I feel so sorry for these bastards that I'll even help you a little...
	Here, take this coin along with you.
	I still make a profit every damn time I dig your grave.
#purgatory_gravedigger_welcome_02
	Some say to truly wake up from the dream, you gotta die within it.
	That's why you gotta bring "some tool" with you...
	An item to shorten your damn "health bar", if you catch my drift.
#purgatory_gravedigger_eye
	You got a damn hole in your skull, but you can use this eye to examine stuff.
