#purgatory_victoria_exit_ending
	LOOK!
	We've already made some progress!
	It's not much, but it's hard to try something new.
	I'm happy that we can create our own world at all!
	And it's all thanks to you!
	Unfortunately...
	We can't really repay you.
	Our Creator left this place. 
	Then the painter misused the pen.
	He wanted to draw with a tool designed to write stories.
	I really wish I could give you a better reward.
	But you're holding the pen right now, and that might mean no one else is going to write the rest of the story...
	Well, we'll see.
	We are finally free to live our own lives.
	Now it's time for you to wake up...
	Goodbye my friend!
