	We managed to smuggle the ink into this place.
	But don't worry, ink used by a creative person is a force for good.
	It's only dangerous in the hands of uninspired people.
	They are the ones who use it to write harmful stories, express offensive comments and draw caricatures of reality.
	The characters trapped in this place are  bored, but full of potential and optimism.
	They are just waiting to spread their wings.
	Just put them on the right path and they will find their own ways.
