	Cold Liquids
#purgatory_hospital_eye
	I'm happy to finally meet you.
	I wish I could show up sooner, but I needed you to experience this place.
	Everything here is rotting, a caricature of its former glory.
	But there is still hope...
	Beneath these bloody and ink-soaked pages lies something else.
	The stack of papers is high, and at the very bottom are unused and forgotten ideas.
	They are completely different from here.
	That place was never touched by the destructive energy of ink and self - doubt.
	Down there everything is drawn with an ordinary, boring pencil.
	Uninspired, abandoned sketches.
	It is there that we must seek purpose, because here there is no hope...
	So... I won't waste any more time...
	See you there.
#purgatory_the_end
	The End